import { Box, Button, Container, Grid, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'


export const Ingreso = () => {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth='sm'>
        <Grid item xs={6}>
            <Typography
                variant='h6'
                sx={{mb:1,mt:1}}
            >Inicio de Sesión</Typography>
            <Box component='form' >
                <TextField
                    name='username'
                    fullWidth 
                    label='Email'
                    sx={{mt:2,mb:1.5}}
                    required
                    margin='normal'
                    type='text'
                ></TextField>
                <TextField
                    name='password'
                    fullWidth 
                    label='Contraseña'
                    sx={{mt:2,mb:1.5}}
                    required
                    margin='normal'
                    type='password'
                ></TextField>
                <Button></Button>
            </Box>
        </Grid>
    </Container>
  )
}
